  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a Patchelf</title>

    <para>
      The <application>patchelf</application> package contains a small utility to
modify the dynamic linker and RPATH of ELF executables.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&patchelf-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferncia (FTP): <ulink url="&patchelf-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Soma de verificao MD5: &patchelf-md5sum;
        </para>
